	   <tr><td colspan=2>It is very hard to beat a good enchanter in a duel. Your best bet is to use an air pet and send it right at him. If he has a pet out, don't even worry about it, just focus all your efforts on him. He probably won't have a pet out, however. As soon as the duel starts he will most likely charm your pet and send it at you. <br><br>If starts the match with a pet, then you will have a decent chance to beat him. Just send in your pet(preferably air) on him and nuke, nuke, nuke. <br><br>Its pretty hard to beat an enchanter. They have a lot of variety in their spells, plus charm is a huge advantage.<br><br>Generally speaking, whenever you are fighting someone that has a pet, focus everything on the master, not the pet.<br><br>Former Addict of Evequest.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
